e good work.8. BEARS!!! .... freaking awesome to tap a bear and watch them come running and then slaughter the zombies for us! LOL SWEET!9. Would love more Forged Steel tools. Pickaxe is the only one, but a shovel and better axes should be the progression of tools.This is a deep game, creative crafting and building/upgrading. Decent combat vs zombies as a pure survival game. Just kill them quick..nothing too outlandish. You're trying to survive and this is basic survival.Yes it can get glitchy / buggy, but it's a blast with friends.Keep up the hard work!"
