ly and they will lose a large amount of players for it.The last thing you need to know is that their community site is pretty toxic, if you are not a rabid fanboi then you will be openly insulted, trolled and insulted and this will be ignored by their moderators (some of whom were so dismissive of any negative feedback that even TFP had to fire them eventually).  No feedback will be tolerated if its perceived in any way as negative or not in line with the devs ''vision'', dont take my word for it, go and read their latest A13 dev thread.I have had some amazing times playing this game, particularly with a wide ranging group of friends and particularly in PVP but the direction the devs are taking it now is thevery opposite of that attracted all the people I know in the first place.I have to put in a reccomendation as the game is now rather than as it used to be and for tht reason I cannot reccomend although I hope that the devs do see sense and recognise the huge playerbase of PVP'ers and how important they are to the games success and that they stop dumbing the game down for the console kiddies.Until that happens I have to say i do not reccomend."
