s day and still it's a work in progress. I recommend this game to everyone if you like first person zombie survival horror. It's quite atmospheric in some places where it can turn really quiet and audio of wind and whistles to loud screeching and infected crawling up on you. Be warned it can be a scary game but rather fun one aswellI recommend this to everyone who likes this sort of game remember to look at the trailer so you can have a basic idea what you are stumbling upon.Thank you and I like this game alot!"
