uch has improved that I now accually will recomend this game to people who are interested in a more ""hardcore"" minecrafty survivalgame. This game is great fun and I see a huge potential in it, though it still could use some more optimization. If you are playing the multiplayer you notice that the server can't really handle bigger ammounts of zombies - if your friends allerts a horde in an area far away from you - suddenly there are almost no zombies at where you are. This game still has some work left untill it's complete, but it's getting there and I now consider it much enjoyable."
