76561197994416666,Recommended,251570,9834770,"Posted: 16 April, 2014",all,Schwivid,"I got this game just after I came out, and I have to say, as far as Alphas go, this one should win an award.  I have recommended this game to many of my gaming freinds, and they have all bought it and we play it together often through my easily configured dedicated server.There is something in here for everyone.  If you like killing zombies, mining, building, crafting, and exploring, this is definitely for you.  Nothing is more gratifying than walking up to a zombie and smashing them one in the face with your bare fist.  Or if you're in to guns, 7 days will not disappoint.  Sure, most of the weapons are generic, but whether you like donning  a pistol, or taking out a crowd of zombies with a rocket launcher, then it here.I am also fond of the forging and crafting system.  Once you learn recipes, you can strip down a weapon to its bare parts, create a mold of these parts and then manufacture all the weapons but the rocket launcher.  You can even craft your own bullets using the method described above.I love the two power tools, the chainsaw and the auger.  Not only are these great for gathering wood and stone, but they make quick work of any zombies.This game is filled with pure enjoyment, despite the occasional bug here and there.The Fun Pimps are great at what they do.  Although they have not implemented all the features detailed in the video, they have been consistant at following the road map of development.I would give this game 5 stars, and it, even in alpha I would give it a metacritic rating of 95.Bottom line:  Pure enjoyment! Worth more than just a cursory glance."
