games this one doesnt have to poor graphics and is nice when building or mining btw dont reccomend mining under a house without proper supports becuase the mine may collapse and eventualy wipe out your house. RIP 600 quality chainsaw and auger. There is jsut so much about this game that other games lack that you can get over the bugs. I almsot forgot to add that this is one of those games that dont judge it from the games preview video becease that video is quite outdated and does not represent the current state and many changes have been added a few optimizations from when that video was made. Overall I give the game a 8/10 mainly beucase of the bugs and consider it a must buy for any gamer especialy if your into zombie, survivals, or even zombie survivals.*Forgot to mention if your to terrified to play singleplayer which is reccomended for everyone to try once to learn hte basics before going into multiplayer is multiplayer is great to...just beware of those maniac player who you feel like are high. Also you may find a good pve server and those players may be more than welcome to help you out and give you a friendly welcome and some company in the zombie apocalypse but afterall its all about the fun and game. so if you decide to buy have a great day in the zombie apocalypse.I could go on but I dont want to put to much about the game since its quite the experience that has so much contnent that you wish other games had or understood. Thank you for reading and sorry for any gramatical errors that I made."
