 the game, but there isn't really a later in the game, if that makes sense? Later in the game is pretty much the same stuff, and nothing really to look forward to to other than fending off the horde every 7 days.5. the Zombie interaction does feel a bit secondary. maybe i should play feral all day, but think I'd get frustrated at the amount I would die :-)But all of these could certainly be a 7 Days to Die 2. A really enjoyable game, and am still playing it. Good job!"
