76561198052356668,Recommended,251570,13944454,"Posted: 11 January, 2015",all,karxarinis,"If u like vortex-like games like minecraft you will like this game too. You spawn in a world full of zombies and you carry very inferior items with you. Then you have to search for items that  will help you survive. Like food , tools like a pickaxe , metal scraps and wood. You first craft starter tools that you use to chop down trees and mine rocks or dig  a mine (like minecraft). You spawn at 8 in the morning and you have 12-13 hours to get ready for the night. In the mornig zombies are dangerous but are very slow and you can escape them easily (except of dogs that run fast and are very dangerous even at daylight). However when it gets dark zombies go in a frenzied / god mode. They run faster than you and have a good damage too. They will also hunt you in the buildings or they will start digging until they reach you (if you are underground).  So you have to find a safe place in the night that you can guard. In every ingame day that pass more zombies come in the map and you will often hear schools of zombies walking. So everyday the game gets harder (but you will also have more tools to use). When some days pass the houses and other buildings do not offer enough protections as zombies will break the walls and the they will kill you. So you have to build your own fort. To build the fort you must have advanced materials etc. This game is sanbox that means that the player makes the rules. There is not a clear objective other than survive. When you die you drop everything (there are other options too in settings) in a bag, that stays in the place you died forever (unless another player pick it up ofc).things i likedThis game takes the best parts of minecraft and makes them much better. You find items and you build buildings etc but with much better graphics and zombies  is a real threat with a typical AIIt is sandbox but it does not luck objectives. Player sets the next mission for himself (find X material or weapon)Use your imagination to make a nice fort. Place traps around it and make it tough. Its hard to find 2 same designs.things i didnt likedToo many bugs. Yes its an alpha and blah blah but it is not for free. It is at steam for sale.I bought it mainly because I like play games in an online world. However I didnt enjoy multiplayer at all.Why?Random low fps. As you run in the world your dps drops at 1-3 fps even at lowest video configuration. (my pc plays bf4 at good settings)bad configurations at servers! Most servers take only pvp in account. The zombies are almost non existent and for sure not threatening even at the middle of the night"
